=====================================================
===Collecting Hub Modeling for Community Detection===
=====================================================

fb_main.py is the main file for our experiments.

Run:
To run different experiment, comment/uncomment the bottom of the code for the expected experiment, and run "python fb_main.py" from command line.

Input/Output
The default input path for this file is testdata under the same folder, which is included. 
The output path can be configured, see the code for details

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

fb_metis.py is a utility program for converting fb dataset into METIS format.

Run: 
python fb_metis.py [egonetwork number]
output: fb network structure in METIS format

Dependecies are : networkx, numpy, itertools

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Raw Facebook data is available at http://snap.stanford.edu/data/egonets-Facebook.html
